1
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,620
If he had fallen to his death before me,

2
00:00:19,290 --> 00:00:21,750
I'd have nightmares forever.

3
00:00:28,410 --> 00:00:29,410
Get lost!

4
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,200
Give me your hand.

5
00:01:20,660 --> 00:01:22,040
Xie Xinxu!

6
00:01:23,370 --> 00:01:24,540
What a fool.

7
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:22,910
You surprised me just now.

8
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:24,597
I didn't expect you

9
00:02:24,621 --> 00:02:26,250
to die together with me willingly.

10
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:29,660
That was just an accident.

11
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:30,830
Besides,

12
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,750
I crawled back

13
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:33,226
because I was worried

14
00:02:33,250 --> 00:02:34,226
that you might haunt me in my dreams.

15
00:02:34,250 --> 00:02:35,250
Get it?

16
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:50,500
What was that just now?

17
00:02:51,620 --> 00:02:52,620
An octopus?

18
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:53,750
It's so huge.

19
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,320
It probably mutated after
contacting the Affinity B Virus.

20
00:02:58,410 --> 00:03:01,040
Affinity Virus can also
infect some animals.

21
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,620
However, the chances are low.

22
00:03:03,290 --> 00:03:05,250
So, the Special
Administration Bureau sent Ren

23
00:03:05,450 --> 00:03:06,450
on missions

24
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:08,040
to exterminate mutated animals.

25
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,516
Is it because they will go
berserk and hurt people?

26
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:15,040
Did it

27
00:03:15,410 --> 00:03:16,540
go berserk just now?

28
00:03:16,950 --> 00:03:17,950
Looking at its condition,

29
00:03:18,410 --> 00:03:20,160
it didn't simply go berserk.

30
00:03:21,790 --> 00:03:22,790
It feels more

31
00:03:23,660 --> 00:03:24,980
like someone was manipulating it.

32
00:03:27,620 --> 00:03:28,726
No way.

33
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:31,540
How can humans simply
control the actions of animals?

34
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,370
Genus didn't just

35
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,290
develop inhibitors in the past.

36
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:37,620
It also carried out

37
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:39,000
other kinds

38
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:40,870
of experiments in secret.

39
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,846
[Affinity B]

40
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:49,870
So,

41
00:03:50,250 --> 00:03:52,056
is this an animal that has
mutated after being infected

42
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,120
by the Affinity B Virus?

43
00:03:53,250 --> 00:03:53,767
Yes.

44
00:03:53,791 --> 00:03:55,750
It is the same type of virus inside a Ren.

45
00:03:56,750 --> 00:03:57,347
So,

46
00:03:57,371 --> 00:03:59,476
the superiors requested us to study

47
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,096
if the virus can be used

48
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:03,400
to establish a connection
between them and a Ren's brain.

49
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:04,160
The goal

50
00:04:04,370 --> 00:04:07,000
is to control them with the Ren's mind.

51
00:04:08,250 --> 00:04:09,346
Was the experiment a success?

52
00:04:09,370 --> 00:04:10,370
I'm not sure.

53
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,910
I'm not interested in any
experiments unrelated to you.

54
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:19,267
However,

55
00:04:19,291 --> 00:04:21,620
I heard they picked a Ren

56
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,120
called Nan Xing.

57
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:25,160
He formed a connection with this animal.

58
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,910
So is this octopus controlled by Nan Xing?

59
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:30,250
Oh.

60
00:04:31,370 --> 00:04:32,500
Both of you found out.

61
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:41,500
Mr. Gu,

62
00:04:41,660 --> 00:04:42,750
it has been so long.

63
00:04:43,250 --> 00:04:44,250
I'm surprised.

64
00:04:44,410 --> 00:04:45,620
You are actually

65
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,410
one of us.

66
00:04:47,790 --> 00:04:48,790
Do you want to join us?

67
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,290
Don't act familiar with me.

68
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,750
We aren't close.

69
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,476
[Gu Yanqing]
What do you actually want?

70
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:55,180
Naturally, it's to get rid of both of you.

71
00:04:55,370 --> 00:04:56,370
Besides,

72
00:04:57,370 --> 00:04:59,040
my baby is starving.

73
00:05:04,700 --> 00:05:05,700
Also,

74
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:07,040
I'm hungry as well.

75
00:05:11,410 --> 00:05:12,040
Miss,

76
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:13,620
why don't you become my Yin?

77
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,000
Then,

78
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,596
I can consider

79
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:18,000
sparing the remaining people.

80
00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:22,540
So,

81
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:23,870
what's your choice?

82
00:05:24,790 --> 00:05:25,790
I get it.

83
00:05:26,620 --> 00:05:28,500
If you can't think of an answer,

84
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:30,030
we'll just have to get rid of

85
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:32,000
the person who asked the question.

86
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:39,500
Don't move!

87
00:05:41,410 --> 00:05:42,410
Xie Xinxu.

88
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:47,500
As you already know,

89
00:05:47,910 --> 00:05:49,620
as soon as I think about it,

90
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,000
my baby will strangle
her to death immediately.

91
00:05:57,830 --> 00:05:58,870
She formed a pact with me.

92
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,040
She is exclusive to me.

93
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,820
Even if you get her, it's no use.

94
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,410
If you can defeat me,

95
00:06:08,910 --> 00:06:11,250
that means you have high
viral load in your blood, right?

96
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:12,790
Why don't you

97
00:06:13,250 --> 00:06:14,620
let my baby suck your blood?

98
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:15,597
Perhaps

99
00:06:15,621 --> 00:06:17,000
it can become stronger.

100
00:06:22,790 --> 00:06:24,120
That sounds

101
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,910
like a great deal.

102
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:30,580
Xie Xinxu!

103
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:32,700
Deal.

104
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:51,870
Xie Xinxu!

105
00:06:58,410 --> 00:06:59,410
Enough.

106
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,250
You need a balanced diet.

107
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:02,660
Don't overeat.

108
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,000
No.

109
00:07:06,410 --> 00:07:07,870
This is far from enough.

110
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,250
Xie Xinxu, you madman.

111
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:18,500
Are you trying

112
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,250
to pump my baby full of your virus?

113
00:07:44,370 --> 00:07:45,250
Stop!

114
00:07:45,370 --> 00:07:47,000
If you keep losing blood, you will die.

115
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,160
Don't worry.

116
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:50,500
Right now,

117
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:53,250
I'm going to burst from excitement.

118
00:07:55,410 --> 00:07:56,700
Do you want to calm me down?

119
00:07:58,370 --> 00:07:59,620
How do I calm...

120
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,290
Next time,

121
00:08:57,370 --> 00:08:59,540
I want you to calm me
in a more intense way.

122
00:09:01,540 --> 00:09:02,540
We just

123
00:09:02,620 --> 00:09:04,200
exchanged saliva.

124
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:07,870
I hope we didn't form a pact.

125
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,120
That's impossible.

126
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,870
An official pact

127
00:09:12,370 --> 00:09:14,660
will never be so dull.

128
00:09:14,830 --> 00:09:16,830
The virus in the saliva
isn't that concentrated...

129
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:19,870
Xie Xinxu!

130
00:09:23,410 --> 00:09:24,410
There's a way

131
00:09:24,700 --> 00:09:25,700
on this platform

132
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:28,790
that leads to the transport hub.

133
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:36,660
Mr. Ding.

134
00:09:36,870 --> 00:09:37,976
What have you done!

135
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,096
Why did you move the crane arm away

136
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,620
before Mr. Gu was here?

137
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:41,227
Yes.

138
00:09:41,251 --> 00:09:42,410
Nongyu wasn't there either.

139
00:09:42,620 --> 00:09:43,620
What's that attitude?

140
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:45,710
The group of Ren almost
caught up to the arm.

141
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:46,290
If he hadn't moved it,

142
00:09:46,370 --> 00:09:47,766
all of us would have been dead.

143
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:49,726
[Under Maintenance]
Moreover, Gu Yanqing and his intern

144
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:50,750
might have already...

145
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,370
- Don't jinx it!
- Don't jinx it!

146
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:54,596
If you have time to discuss
something that happened,

147
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:57,040
why not think of a way
to activate this train?

148
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:58,726
We should escape

149
00:09:58,750 --> 00:09:59,870
before those Ren catches up.

150
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,636
Carry him inside the carriage first.

151
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:12,660
Let's go.

152
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:26,870
Mr. Gu is badly hurt.

153
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,290
How come you are unscathed?

154
00:10:29,660 --> 00:10:30,660
Enough.

155
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:33,280
Thankfully, there are
emergency medical supplies here.

156
00:10:33,370 --> 00:10:34,476
I need to do a blood transfusion.

157
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:35,160
All of you, go out.

158
00:10:35,161 --> 00:10:39,345
(Watch on www.kissasia.co, .be, .org, .net, .id, .xyz )

159
00:10:35,370 --> 00:10:36,910
Move.

160
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:58,350
[Affinity]

161
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:04,500
How are you? Are you hurt?

162
00:11:39,850 --> 00:11:42,270
[Genus Biological Research Lab Station]

163
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:53,680
[Do not hold doors]

164
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,540
How's Mr. Gu?

165
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:08,120
Don't worry.

166
00:12:08,370 --> 00:12:09,500
He won't die with me around.

167
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:14,500
Mr. Ding.

168
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,386
What happened to your face?

169
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:17,410
I...

170
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:18,870
I...

171
00:12:19,370 --> 00:12:20,370
I have a toothache.

172
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:26,910
Wait.

173
00:12:27,660 --> 00:12:28,477
Tell everyone

174
00:12:28,501 --> 00:12:30,660
not to disturb Gu's rest in the carriage.

175
00:12:33,370 --> 00:12:34,370
That includes you.

176
00:12:37,370 --> 00:12:38,370
You, come with me.

177
00:12:51,950 --> 00:12:54,040
Do you already know
that Gu Yanqing is a Ren?

178
00:12:57,540 --> 00:13:00,000
That kid doesn't know how
to respect elders and juniors.

179
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,160
What's wrong?

180
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:22,350
You...

181
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:23,500
Sorry.

182
00:13:25,870 --> 00:13:27,120
He is a threat now.

183
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:29,386
He will go berserk without the inhibitors.

184
00:13:29,410 --> 00:13:30,516
Thankfully, Li Mo and the rest

185
00:13:30,540 --> 00:13:31,910
found a way to activate the train.

186
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:33,250
To be safe,

187
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:34,750
he should be left here.

188
00:13:35,540 --> 00:13:37,660
He went berserk to save me and the others.

189
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,000
At...

190
00:13:39,370 --> 00:13:40,370
At least...

191
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:42,096
We should find an inhibitor before we leave

192
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,136
to turn him back to normal, at least.

193
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,290
Inhibitor?

194
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:46,820
All the inhibitors were taken
away by the group of Ren.

195
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:47,976
Are you thinking about...

196
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,120
I'll search for one with him

197
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:50,886
while ensuring his safety.

198
00:13:50,910 --> 00:13:51,290
No.

199
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:52,096
I can do it.

200
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,120
I must give it a try.

201
00:14:00,370 --> 00:14:01,570
I'll give you an hour at most.

202
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:04,580
After an hour, the train will depart.

203
00:14:52,620 --> 00:14:53,620
Gu Yanqing,

204
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:56,000
you want it, right?

205
00:14:56,410 --> 00:14:57,500
I am an Yin.

206
00:14:58,370 --> 00:15:00,660
I'm willing to relieve your pain.

207
00:15:09,370 --> 00:15:10,370
Mr. Gu,

208
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:13,250
since the day I became your assistant,

209
00:15:13,790 --> 00:15:16,370
I stopped falling for someone else.

210
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:20,790
I was worried that I couldn't be with you,

211
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,500
until I discovered

212
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,540
you are a Ren.

213
00:15:25,410 --> 00:15:27,540
A Ren and an Yin make a perfect match.

214
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,200
Get lost!

215
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,596
If you don't form a pact with me today,

216
00:15:57,620 --> 00:15:59,500
I'll tell everyone

217
00:15:59,660 --> 00:16:00,660
that you are a Ren.

218
00:16:01,950 --> 00:16:02,950
Do you think

219
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:05,040
everyone will rush here and kill you

220
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:06,870
when you're weak?

221
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:44,476
Let go!

222
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:44,910
Xie...

223
00:16:45,370 --> 00:16:46,370
Mr. Gu.

224
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:57,226
I hate her smell.

225
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:58,250
Shut up.

226
00:16:59,890 --> 00:17:02,350
♪ City lights, hazy lines ♪

227
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:03,750
Get her to leave.

228
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:07,536
♪ Accomplices in passion ♪

229
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:09,266
♪ Shared a sweet damnation ♪

230
00:17:09,290 --> 00:17:10,386
Mr. Gu

231
00:17:10,410 --> 00:17:12,370
is hot-tempered when he's hurt.

232
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:15,410
He has gone berserk.

233
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:17,136
No one here can help him

234
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,250
but me.

235
00:17:19,120 --> 00:17:20,120
Are you an Yin too?

236
00:17:21,430 --> 00:17:22,930
♪ Watch the game ♪

237
00:17:24,410 --> 00:17:25,910
Don't hand me over to her.

238
00:17:26,850 --> 00:17:28,310
♪ Just name ♪

239
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:31,096
♪ Who should be blamed ♪

240
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:31,636
What a coincidence.

241
00:17:31,660 --> 00:17:32,660
I'm also an Yin.

242
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:33,847
Moreover,

243
00:17:33,871 --> 00:17:35,500
I already formed a pact with Mr. Gu.

244
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:38,016
Please give us some space

245
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:39,660
so that I can calm him down.

246
00:17:42,890 --> 00:17:45,946
♪ I see inferno, can't get enough ♪

247
00:17:45,970 --> 00:17:48,446
♪ Burning city, fiery love ♪

248
00:17:48,470 --> 00:17:51,680
♪ It's a fervor, not a crush ♪

249
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:28,720
I...

250
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:30,810
Let me check what's going on.

251
00:18:55,130 --> 00:18:57,740
♪ You smell like something strange ♪

252
00:18:59,200 --> 00:18:59,756
♪ Like wood ♪

253
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:00,547
♪ Like wine ♪

254
00:19:00,571 --> 00:19:02,700
♪ Like the fading rain ♪

255
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:06,626
♪ It's not a problem I can fix ♪

256
00:19:06,650 --> 00:19:10,030
♪ Maybe I'm just meant to be your toy ♪
